    </item>
    <item>
      <title>[부음] 권태순 별세 외</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2024/09/07/PZYT65GBK5BZNHDGNGSESQH4OI/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2024/09/07/PZYT65GBK5BZNHDGNGSESQH4OI/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
